if test_list.length === 1
  p The offered solution should comply with clause #{test_list[0].number}.
else
  p
    | The offered solution should comply with clauses 
    each item, i in test_list
      if i < test_list.length - 2
        | #{item.number}, 
      else if i == test_list.length - 2
        | #{item.number} 
      else
        | and #{item.number}.